Hyperiums is an online browser game.
You have planets and you can make some trades between planets.
Each planet has a type in this list : Agro, Minero, Techno
Trades rules are simple : 
 - Each planet has a number of unit to trade (player can buy new units for the planet)
 - Planets of the same type can't make trades
 - If planet "A" is trading with planet "B" 2 units, both planet have 2 units used 
